race.comment: FLYING ADLER (3) turned in a moderate effort last time when sixth at this track over 350m behind Angry Franky (19.87) in a Grade 5. Strong form has emerged from his last run. Ready to return to form. BUST UP (1) was safely held last time out, finishing fifth at Geelong over 400m behind Sunny Boy (23.56) in a Grade 5. Placed at his previous run. Can do much better this time. DESTINI PALADIN (6) was below best at his last start when 6th at this track following a third place finish (19.80) there two back. Has a good record here at this journey. Can measure up this time. LAMIA ERNIE (2) can measure up with the right run.
